<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Dynastidae" genus="Chalepides" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Chalepides" order="Coleoptera" pageId="48" pageNumber="49" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Chalepides</taxonomicName>
species are attracted to lights at night (
<bibRefCitation author="Kusui, Y" journalOrPublisher="The Nanki Seibutu" pageId="76" pageNumber="77" pagination="64 - 65" title="On a species of the genus Chalepides from the Kii Penisula." volume="34" year="1992">Kusui 1992</bibRefCitation>
